title: Bug 121687: Exception throws when exporting data in table inside a grid cell
description: When exporting data in a table that is inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
OB: An exception is thrown when trying to export data from a table that is inside a grid cell.
EB: The export process should be successful without throwing any exceptions.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Insert a table into a grid cell.
2. Insert another table into another grid cell.
3. Attempt to export the data from one of the tables.
